Package com.example.meditrackr.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CareProvider
    CareProvider: A CareProvider has a list of patients which can be retrieved.
    Comment
    Comment: Stores information about a comment (message) left by a patient or care provider, including the date (timestamp), the text of the message, and the username of the user who left the comment.
    CommentList
    CommentList: A list of comments.
    Patient
    Patient: A Patient has a list of problems which can be retrieved.
    PatientList
    PatientList: A list of patients.
    PlaceInfo
    PlaceInfo: Used for geolocation map activity.
    Problem
    Problem: Stores all information associated with a problem object, including a title, date and description Records have a RecordList, an ImageSave (list of string photo names for storage) and a CommentList
    ProblemList
    RecordList: A list of records.
    Profile
    Profile: Stores all information associated with a profile object, including a username, email, phone and a boolean user type identifies
    ProfileList
    ProfileList: A list of profiles.
